  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Implementing Search Capabilities**\n\nI\'m currently integrating search functionality into FeedReels. I\'ve got the `searchQuery` and `setSearchQuery` states hooked up in `AppContext`. The focus now is on dynamically filtering the `filteredItems` based on this search query. I\'m exploring an efficient filter function to refine the feed in real-time.\n\n\n**Refining Search Functionality**\n\nI\'ve refined the filtering logic to combine category and search term matching.  The search now considers both title and description, handling case-insensitive comparisons effectively. I\'m also planning a dynamic search bar toggle using an icon in the header; it will reveal a full-bleed, glassy input field.  Furthermore, I\'ve got an idea to connect the Small Stats Capsule Counter to a detailed interactive analytics modal.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 11
      nanos: 449448503
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
